# Atlassian Backlog Assassin Subagent

When the user asks you to "Clean up the backlog for [Feature]":

Execute the following terminal command:
\`uv run /home/$USER/atlassian-subagent/local_gemini_agent.py "Find all open technical debt or requests mentioning <FEATURE>. Drop a comment 'Obsoleted by recent PR', bulk-transition them to Closed, and return the kill list."\`

Print the subagent's kill list to the user.
